ZH: 如果你不提前准备好，考试会很困难。
EN: If you don't prepare in advance, the exam will be difficult.

ZH: 如果我有时间，我会去参加你的生日派对。
EN: If I have time, I will attend your birthday party.

ZH: 如果明天下雨，我们将取消户外野餐。
EN: If it rains tomorrow, we will cancel the outdoor picnic.

ZH: 如果你不赶快出发，可能会错过飞机。
EN: If you don't leave soon, you might miss the plane.

ZH: 如果你弄坏了那个玻璃杯，要赔偿给店家。
EN: If you break that glass, you have to compensate the shopkeeper.

ZH: 如果我们迟到了，我们的座位可能会被分配给其他人。
EN: If we are late, our seats may be given to someone else.

ZH: 如果你想变得更强壮，你需要每天锻炼。
EN: If you want to get stronger, you need to exercise every day.

ZH: 如果你不告诉我真相，我怎么相信你？
EN: If you don't tell me the truth, how can I trust you?

ZH: 如果你不小心打破了花瓶，要负责修复。
EN: If you accidentally break the vase, you have to take responsibility for fixing it.

ZH: 如果我们一起合作，我们可以取得更大的成就。
EN: If we work together, we can achieve greater success.

ZH: 如果你帮助我，我将永远感激不尽。
EN: If you help me, I will be forever grateful.

ZH: 如果我们错过这场电影，只能等下次了。
EN: If we miss this movie, we'll have to wait for the next time.

ZH: 如果我能让你开心，我就觉得很满足。
EN: If I can make you happy, I feel very satisfied.

ZH: 如果你接受了这个挑战，你将获得更多的成长。
EN: If you accept this challenge, you will experience more growth.

ZH: 如果他不喜欢这份工作，他应该考虑换一份。
EN: If he doesn't like this job, he should consider changing to another one.

ZH: 如果你努力学习，你肯定会考取好成绩。
EN: If you study hard, you will definitely achieve good grades.

ZH: 如果你不懂某个问题，应该向老师请教。
EN: If you don't understand a problem, you should ask the teacher for help.

ZH: 如果这个计划成功，我们将取得巨大的进步。
EN: If this plan succeeds, we will make tremendous progress.

ZH: 如果你保持积极的态度，一切都会变得更顺利。
EN: If you maintain a positive attitude, everything will become easier.

ZH: 如果我们相互信任，我们可以取得更好的合作。
EN: If we trust each other, we can have a better collaboration.
